name: Still Life with Asparagus
description: This elegant still life by Adriaen Coorte (1697) depicts a simple bundle of white asparagus against a dark background.

name: The Milkmaid
description: This masterpiece by Johannes Vermeer (c. 1660) depicts a domestic servant quietly pouring milk in a Dutch kitchen.

name: Self-Portrait with Grey Felt Hat
description: This striking self-portrait was painted by Vincent van Gogh in the winter of 1887-88 during his time in Paris.
